title: Grateful Dead Live at Silver Stadium on 1988-06-30
description:
Set 1

Box Of Rain-> Cold Rain & Snow, Minglewood Blues, Ramble On Rose, Me & My Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Far From Me, Queen Jane Approximately-> Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Green Onions-> China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Samson & Delilah, Believe It Or Not, Truckin-> He's Gone-> Drums-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Turn On Your Love Light - E: Brokedown Palace

only Green Onions
